# Security Rules

Purpose:

- Protect employee and HR data
- Prevent common Laravel security issues
- Standardize secure development practice
- Improve Cursor AI security consistency

---

# Secret Management

Rules:

- never commit `.env`
- never hardcode API key/token/password
- use environment variable
- use config() outside config file
- separate environment credential per environment

Never commit:

```txt
.env
.env.production
service-account.json
private.key